tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AthleteMetrics (
  athlete_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  weight_lifted DECIMAL,
  reps_completed INT,
  time_taken TIME
);

CREATE TABLE AthleteRecords (
  record_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  athlete_id INT,
  weight_lifted DECIMAL,
  reps_completed INT,
  time_taken TIME,
  date_recorded DATE
);

CREATE TABLE athlete_profiles (
  athlete_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  athlete_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender CHAR(1),
  city VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE workout_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  athlete_id INT,
  date DATE,
  time_start TIME,
  time_end TIME
);
